        "content": "<p>Following up on <span class=\"user-mention silent\" data-user-id=\"19257\">Alya Abbott</span>'s feedback on <a href=\"https://github.com/zulip/zulip/pull/22370\">#22370</a>:</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>Let's try using more standard formatting for the field headings in the modal: regular font at least for the \"Question\" and maybe the options (or maybe bold but not large for both?); I'm also not sure we need the hline. You can post a few options in #design if you aren't sure what looks best.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<p>Here's what it <a href=\"/user_uploads/2/df/T1Q0UJIu_Qweqi5UYUSyPH9o/image.png\">currently looks like</a></p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/2/df/T1Q0UJIu_Qweqi5UYUSyPH9o/image.png\" title=\"currently looks like\"><img src=\"/user_uploads/2/df/T1Q0UJIu_Qweqi5UYUSyPH9o/image.png\"></a></div><p>Here are a few options: <br>\n<a href=\"/user_uploads/2/94/YcD1-M_Zp3aHvYVEg63IhQnm/image.png\">regular font size and weight for both the labels</a> <br>\n<a href=\"/user_uploads/2/62/qLJWC2Jxqz5IGskN-AwMk6PD/image.png\">regular font size but bold weight for both the labels</a> <br>\n<a href=\"/user_uploads/2/c0/r-BR_WMs4oDNYZFz_pAz0Q1K/image.png\">without the hline</a> <br>\n<a href=\"/user_uploads/2/6e/sLet7auycoJY5capO_isrLI_/image.png\">without the hline, but with more space in between instead</a> </p>\n<div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/2/94/YcD1-M_Zp3aHvYVEg63IhQnm/image.png\" title=\"regular font size and weight for both the labels\"><img src=\"/user_uploads/2/94/YcD1-M_Zp3aHvYVEg63IhQnm/image.png\"></a></div><div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/2/62/qLJWC2Jxqz5IGskN-AwMk6PD/image.png\" title=\"regular font size but bold weight for both the labels\"><img src=\"/user_uploads/2/62/qLJWC2Jxqz5IGskN-AwMk6PD/image.png\"></a></div><div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/2/c0/r-BR_WMs4oDNYZFz_pAz0Q1K/image.png\" title=\"without the hline\"><img src=\"/user_uploads/2/c0/r-BR_WMs4oDNYZFz_pAz0Q1K/image.png\"></a></div><div class=\"message_inline_image\"><a href=\"/user_uploads/2/6e/sLet7auycoJY5capO_isrLI_/image.png\" title=\"without the hline, but with more space in between instead\"><img src=\"/user_uploads/2/6e/sLet7auycoJY5capO_isrLI_/image.png\"></a></div><p>Combinations of these are easy to imagine... Would love to hear what looks the best to you! (I personally like the last option the most)</p>",
